[ Built-in : identity ] (v.${project.version})

> Identity command allows you to print and set your user identity properties securely.

    ~ identity
    [ print all the current user properties composing its identity if no arguments. ]

    ~ identity set <key=value> <..>
    [ set the identity properties given as key=value ]

    ~ identity get <key> <..>
    [ print the identity properties with given keys ]